                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable D</hi> 158.) On the 19th pf Nov. be<lb></lb>tween twelve and one o'clock at night, I took the prisoner into custody. I told him I wanted him to go with me to the station—he asked, "What for?"—I said I believed it was for robbing his brother—he said, "Oh, I know now; I will have my revenge."</p>
